Started as the travel blog of several friends, the Traveler quickly became popular, attracting thousands of visitors and contributors across the globe.

You can start your acquaintance with the Traveler from the Home page, where the most recent travel articles and gallery image posts are displayed.

Learn more about each country by reading travel articles in the "Destinations" area. Or simply browse through numerous stunning images in the Gallery, taken by our contributors in the far corners of our planet.
